Module Robotinterface
Package robotinterface.manipulator

Class ManipulatorResult

java.lang.Object
robotinterface.manipulator.ManipulatorResult
public class ManipulatorResult
extends java.lang.Object
Result of a complex movement such as Manipulator.moveWristTo(double, double, double, double, double, double,int,double,double).
